#

Stuffed Pork and Potato Casserole

75 min
$12.5
600 kcal
Difficulty: 30%
Servings: 4

Allergens:

dairysoy

Dietary Tags:

gluten-free

Cuisine:

American

Course:

Dinner

Tags:

casserolecomfort foodeasypork

Description

A comforting casserole filled with tender pork and creamy potatoes, perfect for a family dinner!

Ingredients

  • pork chops: 4
  • potatoes: 4 medium
  • cream of mushroom soup: 1 can (10.5 oz)
  • cheddar cheese: 1 cup shredded
  • onion: 1 small, diced
  • garlic powder: 1 tsp
  • salt: to taste
  • pepper: to taste
  • olive oil: 2 tbsp
